        <p>If the color problem goes away when you select a different source or input, then 1.) you may have a faulty connection (see <a href="#connections">Cable Connections</a>), or 2.) the device connected to the TV may be faulty.</p>
        <p>Otherwise, the problem will either be 1.) an improper picture setting, 2.) a faulty or improper cable connection, or 3.) a faulty printed circuit board.</p>
